@node SEC_HIST
@title "Section J :- History"
@{b}@{u}History@{uu}@{ub}

    v1.0    - First public release.

    v1.01   - Fixed minor bug with the preferences file.

    v1.02   - Default audition tune tempo changed to more suitable speed.

    v1.1    - Software modified to work with PC I/F.
              Presets will not be auditioned if the audition file has not been loaded.
              Software will not crash when MIDI keyboard used to test sounds.
              Preset files are now correctly deleted from disk.
              The "search before preset deletion" routine has been greatly improved.
              Software will correctly receive presets if synth was not turned on when
              SoundPalette was started.
              Warning now given before new banks are loaded.
@endnode
